- y Renewal of the letters of guarantee for the Deputy Chief Executive Of/ficers;
- y Agreement for the sale of SODICA shares between Crédit Agricole Capital Investissement & Finance and Crédit Agricole/uni00A0CIB;
- y Agreement between Crédit Agricole SA and Crédit Agricole/uni00A0CIB on the distribution of the indemnity paid in connection with the transaction regarding the dispute over contributions at the Euribor interbank rate;
- y Amendment No. 2 to the business transfer agreement relating to the transfer of Banking Services Division activities from Crédit Agricole S.A. to Crédit Agricole CIB, in order to negotiate and determine the terms and conditions of the change in the transitional period and the deadline to take into account the delay in the migration schedule.

Detailed information on related party agreements is presented by the Statutory Auditors in their special report, provided in Chapter/uni00A08 of this Universal Registration Document.

In accordance with the provisions of Article L. 225-40-1 of the French Commercial Code, the Board of Directors re-examined the agreements entered into and authorised during previous /financial years that continued to be executed in the course of the /financial year 2022.

