In accordance with § 12.3 of the AFEP-MEDEF Code, an initial meeting was held without executive corporate of/ficers on 23 June 2022. In particular, the members of the Board of Directors discussed how upcoming meetings would take place without the executive corporate of/ficers and the matters they would like to see examined in greater depth at Board meetings.

